Name: statsd-telegraf
Version: 3.2.1.post1
Summary: A fork of pystatsd package with Telegraf-compatible tag support.
Home-page: https://github.com/Granitosaurus/statsd-telegraf
Author: Bernardas AliÅ¡auskas
